    <published>2023-10-18T05:50:39.737Z</published>
    <updated>2023-10-18T05:50:39.737Z</updated>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;h1 id=&quot;bolza问题&quot;&gt;Bolza问题&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;引言&quot;&gt;引言&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最近在学习The financial mathematics of market liquidity 和游戏中物理模拟的一些知识，发现这两个地方都涉及到了Bolza问题，决定单独把这块提取出来说一说。我们这边主要把Bolza问题集中在最小化这个小问题上面: &lt;span class=&quot;math display&quot;&gt;&#92;[
J = &#92;int_{0}^T f_t(x(t)) + g_t(&#92;dot{x}(t))dt
&#92;]&lt;/span&gt; 并且满足边界条件&lt;span class=&quot;math inline&quot;&gt;&#92;(x(0) = a, x(T) = b&#92;)&lt;/span&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    <category term="理论物理" scheme="https://anschen1994.github.io/categories/%E7%90%86%E8%AE%BA%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86/"/>
    
    
